  23,62,"Men fawaali wonkii woo si wanaa emmbere ko ki hattanaa kon gollugol, Deftere no ka Amen Men tabintinii e nder mayre gollal kala gollu…óo, hinde wowla Goonga, kan ka sikke woo alah e nder mu'un, hara kam…ìe …ìe too√±iroytaake uytaneede mo∆¥∆¥i ma…ì…ìe …óin, wanaa fii non …ìeydaneede bon…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  23,63,"Ko woni, …ìer…óe heefer…ìe …ìen no e nder welsindaa- re immorde ndee Deftere, nden wowlaynde Goo- nga kan, e Deftere jippiinde nden e ma…ì…ìe, no woodani …ìe kadi golle goo gaanin …óe …ìe woni …óen e mu'un immorde e keefeeru ko kam…ìe gollata …óe."
  23,64,"Haa si Men leptirii neeminaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen ka ngurdan aduna Lepte …óen √ëalnde Darngal tawa kam…ìe hi…ìe towna hitooji ma…ì…ìe …óin ko …ìe faabnatoo…ìe."
  23,65,"Wi'anee …ìe ka ta∆¥inngol …ìe e Yurmeende Alla nden: "Wata on haacu wata on …óa…ì…ìu faabo e ndee √ëalaande, ko pellet, on marah walloowo mo no ha…óana on immorde e Lepte Alla …óen"."
